title: Houston Snags Game 5 Win and Heads Home One Win Away from World Series Title | Top of the Order

media:group.media:title: Houston Snags Game 5 Win and Heads Home One Win Away from World Series Title | Top of the Order
media:group.media:description:
Jeremy Pena becomes the first shortstop to hit a homer in the World Series. Chas McCormick makes an unbelievable game saving catch at the wall to rob JT Realmuto of extra bases. Justin Verlander earns his first World Series win.
